What you need to know:

The PGA of America stripped the 2022 PGA Championship from Trump National at Bedminster, New Jersey, on Sunday, days after Trump supporters attacked the US CapitolPGA of America chief executive officer Seth Waugh says associating with Trump would be harmful for the organization's brand and its mission to grow and support the sportCritics of the PGA of America move included PGA Tour player Grayson Murray